    <div class="service-detail" style="background: var(--card-bg);">
      <h2>Medical Services</h2>
      <p>Dr. Bluestein uses integrative medicine to identify the source of your pain and the biochemical imbalances that may be making it worse. She utilizes personalized medicine to treat the root cause — not just the symptoms.</p>
      <p>Using cutting-edge testing and the latest research, Dr. Bluestein provides modern treatments including supplements, lifestyle changes, and medications to restore your health in the best way possible.</p>
      <p><strong>Note:</strong> Dr. Bluestein works as an integrative pain medicine consultant in conjunction with your current health care team. All patients must have a primary care physician for emergencies and routine care.</p>

      <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">Conditions We Treat</h3>
