<!-- Coaching Services -->
<section class="section" id="coaching">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="service-detail">
      <h2>Education &amp; Coaching</h2>
      <p>Bendy Bodies offers EduCoaching — a unique process combining personalized information with one-on-one coaching with Dr. Linda Bluestein, MD and Rebecca Gluck, PA-C.</p>
      <p>Joint hypermobility and related conditions are often missed by the standard healthcare system. Our EduCoaching program enables individuals worldwide to benefit from the expertise of the Bendy Bodies team from the comfort of your own home.</p>
      <p>Rebecca Gluck, PA-C brings a unique blend of clinical expertise and a background in leading global education and support programs, enabling her to inform, validate, and support clients as they navigate life with hypermobility.</p>
      <p><strong>Note:</strong> EduCoaching sessions are one-on-one client sessions. These are NOT medical appointments and are not a replacement for your own medical team.</p>

      <h3 class="mt-4 mb-2">What Coaching Covers</h3>
      <div class="conditions-grid">
        <div class="condition-item">Joint Hypermobility</div>
        <div class="condition-item">Ehlers-Danlos Syndromes</div>
        <div class="condition-item">Chronic Pain &amp; Fibromyalgia</div>
        <div class="condition-item">Mast Cell Disease</div>
        <div class="condition-item">Complex Regional Pain Syndrome</div>
        <div class="condition-item">Spinal Arachnoiditis</div>
        <div class="condition-item">Chronic Inflammation</div>
        <div class="condition-item">Back Pain</div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: 28px; display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Coaching Session</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Coaching Portal Login</a>
